---
---
<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 via-indigo-600 to-purple-700 py-20 px-4 text-center relative overflow-hidden group">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] opacity-10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-[1px]"></div>
    
    <!-- Animated Orbs -->
    <div class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-400/30 rounded-full blur-[80px] group-hover:bg-blue-300/40 transition-colors duration-1000 animate-[pulse_6s_ease-in-out_infinite]"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -right-32 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-purple-400/30 rounded-full blur-[80px] group-hover:bg-purple-300/40 transition-colors duration-1000 animate-[pulse_8s_ease-in-out_infinite] animation-delay-1000"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-md tracking-tight">Siap upgrade skill tahun ini?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-50/90 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl font-medium">
            Jangan lewatkan kesempatan emas ini. Daftar sekarang dan mulai perjalanan karir IT-mu bersama DBS Foundation dan Microsoft.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
             <a href="https://www.dicoding.com/codingcamp/registration?ref=4394693" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="relative overflow-hidden text-blue-700 bg-white hover:bg-slate-50 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-white/50 font-bold rounded-xl text-lg px-8 py-4 text-center transition-all shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.02] duration-300">
                <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500/10 to-transparent -translate-x-full hover:animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]"></span>
                <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    Daftar Coding Camp
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 -mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
                </span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.dicoding.com/elevate/registration?ref=4394693" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="relative overflow-hidden text-white border-2 border-white/80 hover:bg-white focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-white/50 hover:text-purple-700 font-bold rounded-xl text-lg px-8 py-4 text-center transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-white hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.02] duration-300">
                <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent -translate-x-full hover:animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]"></span>
                <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                    Daftar METC
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 -mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-medium text-white/80">
            Klik tombol &rarr; kamu akan diarahkan ke pendaftaran resmi Dicoding.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
